nodes.text: The Duchess and the Jedi is an interview with Anna Graves who voiced Duchess Satine Kryze of Mandalore in the television series Star Wars: The Clone Wars. The article also includes a list of the best female characters in the Star Wars universe, such as Leia Organa, Padmé Amidala, Mara Jade, Mon Mothma and Yaddle. It was written by Jonathan Wilkins and published in Star Wars Insider 117.
